<section class="page-hero reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Contact ImperialPaws Pekingese</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Thoughtful communication for puppy availability, applications, and
      responsible placement questions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-content reveal">
  <div class="container narrow reveal">
    <p>
      Thank you for your interest in ImperialPaws Pekingese. We welcome
      thoughtful inquiries from individuals and families who are genuinely
      interested in our puppies, adoption process, and care expectations.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-panel">
      <h2>Best First Step</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about a specific puppy, please review that puppy's detail
        page, the adoption process, and the FAQ before contacting us. Most
        availability, application, tracking, and invoice questions are explained
        on the site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Adoption Applications</h2>
    <p>
      If you are interested in a particular puppy, submit an application from
      that puppy's detail page. If you already applied, use your tracking code
      to check the current status before sending a new message.
    </p>

    <h2>General Inquiries</h2>
    <p>
      For general questions that are not addressed elsewhere, use the contact
      information below when available. We prioritize active applications,
      approved placements, and questions related to current puppy listings.
    </p>

    <% if (
      siteSettings.contact.email ||
      siteSettings.contact.phone ||
      siteSettings.contact.location
    ) { %>
      <div class="contact-details">
        <% if (siteSettings.contact.email) { %>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= siteSettings.contact.email %>"><%= siteSettings.contact.email %></a></p>
        <% } %>

        <% if (siteSettings.contact.phone) { %>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:<%= siteSettings.contact.phone.replace(/[^0-9+]/g, '') %>"><%= siteSettings.contact.phone %></a></p>
        <% } %>

        <% if (siteSettings.contact.location) { %>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= siteSettings.contact.location %></p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="notice-box">
        <p>
          Public contact information has not been posted yet. Contact details
          may be provided to approved applicants during the adoption process.
        </p>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="safety-panel">
      <h2>Buyer Safety Reminder</h2>
      <ul class="trust-list">
        <li>Do not send payment for a public listing before application review and approval.</li>
        <li>Keep your tracking code private.</li>
        <li>Confirm any invoice matches the puppy, buyer details, and agreed amount.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="closing-note">
      We appreciate patient, respectful communication. Responsible placement is
      careful work, and every inquiry is handled with the puppy's well-being in mind.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
